lt=\"Community events\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover opacity-20\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-community.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-community.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-community.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-community.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-community.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-community.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-community.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-community.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-community.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-dem-blue via-dem-blue/95 to-dem-blue-dark/90\"></div></div><div class=\"relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-5xl\">Events</h1><p class=\"mt-4 text-xl text-white/80\">Meetings, volunteer opportunities, and community events</p></div></section><section class=\"py-16 sm:py-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><h2 class=\"mb-8 text-2xl font-bold text-dem-blue\">Upcoming Events</h2><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-dem-gray-200 bg-white shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row\"><div class=\"flex shrink-0 flex-col items-center justify-center bg-dem-red p-6 text-white sm:w-32\"><span class=\"text-3xl font-bold\">14</span><span class=\"text-sm font-medium uppercase\">Mar</span><span class=\"text-sm\">2026</span></div><div class=\"flex-1 p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-dem-gray-900\">Monthly Central Committee Meeting</h3><div class=\"mt-2 flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm text-dem-gray-600\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg>6:00 PM</span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z\"></path><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1115 0z\"></path></svg>Ukiah Valley Conference Center, Ukiah, CA</span></div><div class=\"prose prose-sm mt-4 max-w-none\"><p>Join us for our monthly Central Committee meeting. We'll discuss upcoming elections, community organizing efforts, and hear from local candidates. All registered Democrats are welcome to attend.</p>\n<p><strong>Agenda includes:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Committee business and reports</li>\n<li>Guest speakers</li>\n<li>Campaign updates</li>\n<li>Community action items</li>\n<li>Open forum</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div></div></div><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-dem-gray-200 bg-white shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row\"><div class=\"flex shrink-0 flex-col items-center justify-center bg-dem-red p-6 text-white sm:w-32\"><span class=\"text-3xl font-bold\">11</span><span class=\"text-sm font-medium uppercase\">Apr</span><span class=\"text-sm\">2026</span></div><div class=\"flex-1 p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-dem-gray-900\">Voter Registration Drive</h3><div class=\"mt-2 flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm text-dem-gray-600\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg>10:00 AM - 2:00 PM</span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z\"></path><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1115 0z\"></path></svg>Alex Thomas Plaza, Ukiah, CA</span></div><div class=\"prose prose-sm mt-4 max-w-none\"><p>Join fellow Democrats as we hit the streets to register voters! The June 2026 primary election is approaching and we need every eligible citizen registered and ready to vote.</p>\n<p><strong>What to bring:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Comfortable walking shoes</li>\n<li>Water bottle</li>\n<li>Enthusiasm for democracy!</li>\n</ul>\n<p>All materials will be provided. No experience necessary — we'll train you on the spot.</p>\n</div></div></div></div><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-dem-gray-200 bg-white shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row\"><div class=\"flex shrink-0 flex-col items-center justify-center bg-dem-red p-6 text-white sm:w-32\"><span class=\"text-3xl font-bold\">16</span><span class=\"text-sm font-medium uppercase\">May</span><span class=\"text-sm\">2026</span></div><div class=\"flex-1 p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-dem-gray-900\">Annual Blue Wave Fundraiser Dinner</h3><div class=\"mt-2 flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm text-dem-gray-600\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg>5:30 PM</span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z\"></path><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1115 0z\"></path></svg>Mendocino County Fairgrounds, Ukiah, CA</span></div><div class=\"prose prose-sm mt-4 max-w-none\"><p>Save the date for our Annual Blue Wave Fundraiser Dinner! This is our biggest event of the year and a wonderful opportunity to come together as a community.</p>\n<p><strong>Evening includes:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Cocktail reception</li>\n<li>Dinner</li>\n<li>Keynote speaker</li>\n<li>Silent auction</li>\n<li>Live music</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Tickets and sponsorship information coming soon. Contact us for details.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-dem-blue-dark text-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-16\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-2\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">Mendocino County Democratic Central Committee</h2><address class=\"mt-4 not-italic leading-relaxed text-white/70\"><p>PO Box 28</p><p>Ukiah, CA 95482</p></address><div class=\"mt-6 flex items-center gap-4\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Mendodems/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white/10 p-2.5 text-white transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-white/20\" aria-label=\"Follow us on Facebook\"><svg class=\"h-5 w-5\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M22 12c0-5.523-4.477-10-10-10S2 6.477 2 12c0 4.991 3.657 9.128 8.438 9.878v-6.987h-2.54V12h2.54V9.797c0-2.506 1.492-3.89 3.777-3.89 1.094 0 2.238.195 2.238.195v2.46h-1.26c-1.243 0-1.63.771-1.63 1.562V12h2.773l-.443 2.89h-2.33v6.988C18.343 21.128 22 16.991 22 12z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://cadem.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-sm font-m